tourBios.carHigh:
2015: Appeared destined to not earn his PGA TOUR China Series' playing privileges after opening 74-79-79 at the Second Global Qualifying Tournament at CTS Tycoon GC in Shenzhen. Then fashioned a final-round, 3-under 69 that included three birdies in his final five holes, to earn conditional status. 

2014: Played one Japan Golf Tour event, the PGA Championship Nissin Cupnoodles Cup, missing the cut.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA Tour China Serie was T18th in 2015 at the The Eternal Courtyard Open.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks 65th in Scoring Average (Actual) on the PGA Tour China Series.
